{
  "stem": "9489.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You want it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I says, what you mean by that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Why not a job like that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, that's going to be the second front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's worse like the front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we go in, in the second front.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's more danger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The airplanes, the artillery, and they know the second front is worse, like the first front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't have choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I liked the guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So right away, I got in, in-- in the barracks specially, from these big shots-- beautiful restaurant, ice cream, you name it, it was there, served like a king.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Uniform-- you saw my uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we got our training.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We got our vehicles after the America.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then they sent us away to Poland via train, to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then they put us in the bushes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the bushes, we organized in the artillery, the [NON-ENGLISH], what they trust to Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But they give it to us three.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the train, me and another two guys-- one was Grossman, a lieutenant, is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His father on-- is from Prague, Czechoslovakia-- owns the factory from Messerschmitt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK, I'll tell you about him in a second.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I ask him, how you survive?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- I come, you come to Polish army?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When Germany invade Czechoslovakia, his father gave him airplane to run away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His father didn't want to run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm telling you the way honest, you know, the way he told me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Very nice looking guy, very intelligent-- and he to over the plane.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he fall down in Poland, besides Ternopil, in [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Bitze, ?] in-- behind enemy line, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was then German occupied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He line up there, in a village, like close to a village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he fall down with the plane there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got wounded.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
